abstract: New Jersey Transit pre-emptively announces residual delays to Monday morning service, recommending alternative services; announcement comes less than week after NJT suffered three consecutive days of delays caused by electrical problems.
lead_paragraph: The transportation agency on Sunday preemptively announced “residual delays” to its Monday morning service.

headline.main: N.J. Transit Announces More Delays Amid Work
